reviewText: Poor quality. Never received whole order

So, so funny.  Wish they had more updated material on Flowers & Madame.  So much talent!  I've seen them in person here in Las Vegas, Nevada.  You laugh so hard you can miss the next joke!!  This was not his best work, but funny.  He had so many other charaters too.  Was featured on Hollywood Squares and Andy Williams late at night.
Very poorly taped show of the two.  The film quality is so poor you can barely see their faces, making it fairly worthless.
